{"tid":2130912,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】林秀怡公開「黑歷史」　回顧讀書MK造型大呼︰好恐怖啊！","createTime":"2020-07-29T13:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T03:20:10.000Z","uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"f695ab1a4eacfdabe1a40e6e837a89218cd9edcc","tid":2130912,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:06:58.000Z","msg":"正所謂「誰人沒有MK過」，女藝人也不例外，日前林秀怡（Kirby）在YouTube拍片公開自己讀書時期的舊照，完全不介意過去的傻氣和素顏樣公開！<br />\n<br />\nKirby在自己的YouTube Channel公開自己的「黑歷史」，跟大家一起看舊相，由小學時期開始看到中學生涯，其實Kirby的樣子沒有太大分別，只是皮膚白了和會打扮化妝了。最搞笑的是她指當時流行臥蠶，所以她故意不睡覺，以為可以「練」到有臥蠶，聽上去都覺得又搞笑又青春。<br />\n<br />\n看到以前的打扮，Kirby也不禁自嘲一番，笑言自己「着到成個師奶咁」，裡面穿了heattech，外面再加件Polo衫，再戴星星鏈和耳環，她大呼︰「好恐怖啊！」她又不斷指自己︰「肥到呢！」、「冇眼皮啦又」，完全沒有底線！之後就開始有「MK頭」出現，即是用頭夾長期夾住瀏海那種，而且當時還未有智能電話，是用小型的那些Nokia手機，簡直是考古時間啊！"},{"pid":"5ea7ada7b95967f50608f7c1431f3407717a3ebb","tid":2130912,"uid":16659,"like":15,"dislike":8,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200729/365180172103716864.jpeg/Q4_ikCX696AI9zhkdpy6wgRo4R4KQRW3IdFPqiHRT6o?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200729%2F365180172103716864.jpeg%2FQ4_ikCX696AI9zhkdpy6wgRo4R4KQRW3IdFPqiHRT6o%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7c067e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200729/365180425343209472.jpeg/kMU1QXDBhe2c-NlR5fKcOE8a1aIhkTpkuwb1rbsG9a0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200729%2F365180425343209472.jpeg%2FkMU1QXDBhe2c-NlR5fKcOE8a1aIhkTpkuwb1rbsG9a0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=558351a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200729/365180426983182336.jpeg/aWN3uvUV_0ZQCFYxAH8ZZf0V0BnBa8QNccgWO3HIFjs?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200729%2F365180426983182336.jpeg%2FaWN3uvUV_0ZQC